text:
💡Help your child use their fingers, talk about clothes, and organise them! 

Help your child exercise their fingers by showing them how buttons and zips work on clothes, and letting them practise using them! 👋
;
🔵 Talk about the colours of clothes! Ask your child to pick a colour and talk about all the things that are that colour: “What are all the things we can think of that are blue?”
;
😃 Encourage your child to help you sort clothes into piles for each family member.
